    "reading_two": "",
    "psalm_proverb": "Psalm 12",
    "summary": "The Philistine giant Goliath defies Israel’s armies, and no one dares face him, until the shepherd boy David comes in the name of the Lord. With a sling and a stone he defeats the giant, showing that the battle belongs to God. Israel is delivered through unlikely faith.",
