    "summary": "Fleeing for his life, David receives bread and Goliath's sword from the priest Ahimelech at Nob, then escapes to Gath. But Saul, in his paranoia, has Doeg slaughter the priests of Nob, and only Abiathar survives. The cost of Saul's jealousy grows ever darker.",
