    "reading_two": "",
    "psalm_proverb": "Psalm 63",
    "summary": "When the harsh and foolish Nabal insults David, David sets out for revenge, but Nabal's wise wife Abigail intervenes with humility and generosity, restraining David from bloodshed. He blesses God for sending her to keep him from sin. God uses a peacemaker to turn David from rash anger.",
