    "reading_two": "1 Chronicles 1",
    "psalm_proverb": "Psalm 13",
    "summary": "Instead of rejoicing, David mourns deeply for Saul and Jonathan, composing a lament for the fallen king and his beloved friend. In Chronicles, the genealogies begin all the way back at Adam, tracing God's faithfulness across the generations. David grieves with a generous heart, even for the one who hunted him.",
